      <title>中东紧张局势导致股市下跌，国债上涨：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中东紧张局势升级导致全球股市暴跌，并刺激了对债券和美元等避险资产的需求，周五市场仍处于紧张状态。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 22:18:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>吉利将出售价值13.2亿美元的沃尔沃卡车股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/china-s-geely-to-sell-entire-1-32-billion-stake-in-volvo-trucks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，有消息称中国浙江吉利控股集团出售了其全部 B 类股票，价值约 141 亿瑞典克朗（13 亿美元），卡车制造商沃尔沃 AB 的股价周五在斯德哥尔摩下跌 5.9%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/china-s-geely-to-sell-entire-1-32-billion-stake-in-volvo-trucks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 16:44:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
